{d \over dx} e^{f(x)} = f'(x)e^{f(x)}</math>.

:<math>
\begin{align}
\frac{\mbox{d}\ e^x}{\mbox{d}x}&=\lim_{\Delta x\to0}\frac{e^x-e^{x-\Delta x}}{\Delta x}\\
&=e^x\lim_{\Delta x\to0}\frac{1-e^{-\Delta x}}{\Delta x}\\
&=e^x
\end{align}
</math>

